Subject: drm/i915: Polish intel_atomic_track_fbs()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: e3b4089c68ed59fcda9220db02c8ccfe9c49ccd7
